sub_title: Public international lawyer, Member of the New York Bar - Temple Garden Chambers (Associate Member)
summary: Public international lawyer trained in France, Germany and the United States, with substantial experience in the field of inter-State litigation at the highest level. Advises States and other actors on issues of public international law. Specializes in proceedings before the International Court of Justice (ICJ), the International Criminal Court (ICC) and Human Rights bodies. Speaks French, English, Spanish, Dutch and German.
